    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1TextureSet" kindref="compound">TextureSet</ref> is a handle to an object that specifies the set of images used as textures by a renderer. The images have to be ordered in the same order they are declared in the shader. @SINCE_1_1.43. </para>
    </briefdescription>
